    "feat": {
        "name": "Terra Dragonblood",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Each step upon the earth makes your blood resonate. You gain tremorsense as an imprecise sense to a range of 30 feet; if you already have tremorsense, increase its range by 5 feet. If you choose a draconic exemplar, you must choose a dragon with a burrow Speed.",
